{"tid":1340811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗暴亂必須聚焦警黑合作","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:43:06.000Z","uid":170199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"96ee429edb1111f5f7e4ab30b0adacf95a255117","tid":1340811,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"雖然大家都好嬲 但不能跌落港共圈套 變成群眾鬥群眾<br />\n我地要將焦點放在警黑合作<br />\n<br />\n鬥羸牛屎佬雖然重要 但港共同黑警先係真正敵人 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警應該會以港島示威令人手短缺為由解釋<br />\n<br />\n我地必須清晰地表達<br />\n<br />\n1. 追究警察失職 縱容黑社會橫行 危害市民人身安全<br />\n<br />\n2. 政府必須嚴打黑社會 以暴動罪起訴黑社會 以社團條例禁止相關社團活動"},{"pid":"808f050b86a05da7cafda7c973b0b48e0874720f","tid":1340811,"uid":70650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ef6bc14526f7edea3b298c3d7e74bc3ba695f3","tid":1340811,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"31a043279aa71393ec1e2d5a55f14682fefcebf8","tid":1340811,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:25:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"98077e86b85347565492c8f2ecae8e2b907b0e0a","tid":1340811,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"再推"}]}